  "hashesWithUnresolvedText": {
    "95310466d48400744d2f3747794f7b9b8b055f432ebf09590202584ab52c0032": {
      "text": "Hey, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "9f755d8d8afe33673958273e3b5b710269ec168093152bf095f2c0d14cf72680": {
      "text": "But dat not a problem, [player name]. My Arm know lots 'bout growing goutweed. It gonna be fine.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "014b9953f5d5cc616d0368544633548545b9808f7a9a106bec90d11a962f8326": {
      "text": "Eh, [player name], My Arm thinks dis human kinda dumb. Can we use boat or not? My Arm getting bored.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "606dc718bf503030bddf4e8ee34b43d611c79e5465e5c5fbfc9c33d28ae33472": {
      "text": "T'anks, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "73cdb2b62ef1b400db8ee874dcd3e040c1e43c588be371f91d7aba3e8eda728d": {
      "text": "T'anks, Mother. [player name] is helpful human.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "073b7d2397fe0130e219d6a5227ccd3f9e4ffbc0a1479c91de939208b03ccd2d": {
      "text": "Oh... [player name]... look!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "de5aae223789b2e0cbcff3069966f626cf594e68c8a925b8ddd9dda20185fab3": {
      "text": "Uh... [player name], what do we do now? If he kick us out, My Arm never gonna see Snowflake again. Help!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "51bbac88ad9fd0f7c90f6d58070cf9d931c51fbd5c83ba173f6f90c48b199809": {
      "text": "[player name]?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "01f46f139ba11401c66936f2648395c3dcb3681718fa83adfa21d13e65a98194": {
      "text": "Yeah, we really good at combat. Trolls near Stronghold, dey chuck rocks really hard. An' My Arm helped [player name] save da goutweed patch from big flappy bird thing!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "b1b76d53c6ed01f2295b249218c2b26fbdb475f3edf2794ab04fb79edcdf7d2f": {
      "text": "What we do now, [player name]?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "f9cde98926c63eab3d434241119be3df03f64488e0e00ca31d9c619f81ad0d35": {
      "text": "Dis not working, [player name]!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "665fad2c12c2fae6ef5e0acaa7eed616e0fa1c31f223dd29eac0b8409c2058de": {
      "text": "Oh, [player name], My Arm is being sent home. Stupid big Mother not interested in goutweed. My Arm would prefer to stay with Snowflake.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "63a38f604790795161a4ec00314fc4362ff519f4750417c799e0eb8ebc637e51": {
      "text": "Dat a shame. But he know you, [player name], an' you helped him in fishy colony place. Maybe you ask him a favour now?",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "8e205276476799dc848128d20d7e05040d7adf084b87dd62d42c4477c685dbbd": {
      "text": "He very obliging, dis mortal enemy of Weiss. Must have been big favour he owed [player name]. Okieday, give coffin to My Arm, an' My Arm give him to Mother.",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "ad5cc0f670d4769b116a1ab87f2997adf5250f3cbe9c9d979027ead9001e430c": {
      "text": "You good friend, [player name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "6610975c958b154474f4800fcf0aafc93190ec59c6a37a5554a78ac3abcb3e91": {
      "text": "[player name] is brave human an' good friend for My Arm and Snowflake!",
      "placeholders": [
        "[player name]"
      ]
    },
    "127ee29f7de77972e6458d10c3f6f3d2835690deb597c8559e802e7fb8ee2850": {
      "text": "Well, I seen worse. Most humans come through here, dey got names with like all numbers and things wot aren't even words! I met some man earlier wot called himself [other player's name].",
      "placeholders": [
        "[other player's name]"
      ]
    },
    "bef18737ae246778500f9afa27bd1d17b77644907d5dabf295d0dba6f6ea515f": {
      "text": "Well, I seen worse. Most humans come through here, dey got names with like all numbers and things wot aren't even words! I met some woman earlier wot called himself [other player's name].",
      "placeholders": [
